#=======================================================================
#
# README
#
# The script to do failure analysis is mfg_parse.pl
# The bash script mfg_parse.sh copies logs from /mfg_log/
# on MFG server (192.168.3.2) and calls mfg_parse.pl
# 
# 1. Copy the latest mfg_parse.sh to /home/mfg/mfg_diag_fa/
# directory on MFG server
# 2. Copy the latest mfg_parse.pl to /home/mfg/mfg_diag_fa/scripts/
# directory on MFG server
# 3. Then in /home/mfg/mfg_diag_fa/, put all the SNs that need
# parsing into a file, one SN per line
# 4. Run the mfg_parse.sh script with the syntax below:
#    Syntax: mfg_parse.sh [-c|s|f|l|h]
#            options:
#            c     card_type
#            s     stage
#            f     FA option: first/last/all
#            l     SN file
#            h     print this help
#    Example:
#    ./mfg_parse.sh -c ORTANO2 -s 4c-h -f last -l ./sn_list.txt
# 5. The output is parse_rersult.xlsx in the same directory
#=======================================================================

